          <h2 style="             
              font-size: 20px;
              line-height: 1.2;
              font-weight: 500;
              margin-top: 2px !important;">Indonesia releases Bali 9</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-image padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.presidentialsummary.com/email/images/ps-dec-16-2.jpg" alt="Indonesia releases Bali 9" href="https://www.presidentialsummary.com" />
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4; filter: blur(5px)">The remaining members of Bali Nine drug traffickers, nine Australians <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/australia-news/2024/dec/15/final-five-members-of-bali-nine-released-from-jail-and-back-in-australia-pm-announces" target="_blank">arrested</a> in 2005 for attempting to smuggle heroin from Bali, have been returned to Australia after serving over 19 years in Indonesian prisons. Two members of the gang were executed in 2015, while others served lengthy sentences. Australian Prime Minister Anthony Albanese expressed gratitude to Indonesian President Prabowo Subianto for his compassion and reaffirmed Australia’s commitment to combating drug trafficking with Indonesia. The Bali Nine were charged with smuggling 8.3kgs of heroin from Indonesia in 2005.</p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4; filter: blur(5px)">
          The men will not serve further prison time in Australia, and they are expected to continue rehabilitation efforts. In addition, a Filipino woman who was <a href="https://apnews.com/article/indonesia-philippines-transfer-of-prisoner-agreement-b1b39f23b223fe8fcc6bfa07f57cc52b" target="_blank">supposed</a> to be executed the same day as the two Bali nine members but was spared minutes before her scheduled execution was also released earlier this month. Indonesia’s strict drug laws include the death penalty for traffickers, a policy that sparked global attention and tensions, particularly with Australia.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="10px 12px" />
